data.description: Great opportunity in Idaho Creek ! Nice 3 bedroom 2 bath home close to everything. New Vinyl Windows and French Door, Newer Lennox  Furnace and AC, Newer Stainless appliances, Newer AOSmith Water Heater, Upgraded Insulation, Ceiling Fans, Security and Surround Sound Pre Wire, Smart Thermostat. Home undergoing kitchen  renovations but for sale as a work in progress with most materials included  on site. Handy person special in a great neighborhood for a much better price. Please call Marc with any questions.
